page.title: 03ECOLOGY.
page.content: {Important Plants}:Hybrid Orchid,Alder, Buckthorn,Tree Lupin,Strawberry Clover Soft Trefoil Grass,Subterranean Trefoil,Common Earth Star Fungi. {Mammals}:Grey Squirrels,Moles,Rabbits, Hares,Water Shrews,Water Voles. {Amphibians}:Frogs,Toads.{Butterflies: Peacock,Small Tortoiseshell,Red Admiral,Cabbage White,Some Clouded Yellows.{Sea Life}:Sea Gooseberries, Skate Eggs,Mermaid Purses,Star Fish, some Atlantic & Common Seals.{Marshes: Snipe,Lapwings,Yellow Wagtails,Hen Harriers,Barn Owls,Bitterns,Bearded Tits,Marsh Harriers,Shovellers,Gadwell Teals,Mallards{.River}:Sea Lavender, Sea Purslane,Alexanders,Flounders, Mullet, Eels;Ringed Plovers,Dunlin Black Tail Godwits.EASTON BAVENTS:Sand Martins.{Common}:Linnets,Stonechats, Red_backed Shrike.{Gorse}:Linnets.
